message.body: Any chance you would be free this week to: swim, walk, drink, eat, get ice cream... Or any combination of the previous suggestions, or any others I did not mention? I could do any day but Thurs/Fri.
This week is completely 100% batshit insane. Can we schedule swimming for next Monday? That is literally the earliest schedule opening I have

Ha! Sure. Next Monday works... As long as I can steal that "batshit insane" phrase. I'm actually off next Mon for a doctor appointment so my schedule should be fairly flexible tho I may pop into a yoga class around 4-5:30 ish.
Hope the insanity is all good and u aren't too stressed.
Sweet! Let's say Monday, heading for pool at 5:50. :)
